open_embedding_iff_is_iso_comp:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⟶ » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⟶ » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ≫ » -/
@[simp]
theorem open_embedding_iff_is_iso_comp {X Y Z : Top} (f : «expr ⟶ » X Y) (g : «expr ⟶ » Y Z) [IsIso f] :
    open_embedding («expr ≫ » f g) ↔ open_embedding g :=
  by
  constructor
  · intro h
    convert h.comp (Top.homeo_of_iso (as_iso f).symm).open_embedding
    exact congr_arg _ (is_iso.inv_hom_id_assoc f g).symm
  · exact fun h => h.comp (Top.homeo_of_iso (as_iso f)).open_embedding
#align open_embedding_iff_is_iso_comp open_embedding_iff_is_iso_comp

@[simp]
theorem open_embedding_iff_comp_is_iso {X Y Z : Top} (f : «expr ⟶ » X Y) (g : «expr ⟶ » Y Z) [IsIso g] :
    open_embedding («expr ≫ » f g) ↔ open_embedding f :=
  (Top.homeo_of_iso (asIso g)).open_embedding.of_comp_iff f
